# Calendar and Scheduling

## FullCalendar setup

- Pinned version: `@fullcalendar/react@6.1.21` with `@fullcalendar/core`, `daygrid`, `timegrid`, `resource-timeline`, `interaction`
- **Default view:** `resource-timeline` for staff/multi-resource scheduling UI
- Before adding new `@fullcalendar/*` packages: verify peer dependency range includes React 19 and matches `~6.1.21` line

## Data flow

- Calendar event data **always** flows through TanStack Query hooks in `calendar-scheduling/hooks/`
- FullCalendar components **never** fetch directly — receive events as props from query results
- API functions in `calendar-scheduling/api/` use `apiClient` from `src/shared/lib/axios.ts`

## Feature placement

- All calendar UI, hooks, types, and API live under `src/features/calendar-scheduling/` — do not split across other features
